style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><b><span style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>Derini&#328; d&ouml;k&uuml;lmegi&nbsp;</span></b><span
style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>- gaty
kyn bolup bil&yacute;&auml;n, &yacute;agly, sarymtyl tereziler bilen gyzyl
re&#328;kli tegmiller &yacute;aly g&ouml;r&uuml;n&yacute;&auml;r.&nbsp;Nokatlar
birle&#351;m&auml;ge &yacute;ykgyn ed&yacute;&auml;rler.&nbsp;</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:-.25in;line-height:
normal'><span style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;color:black'>·<span
style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>Mationokan&ccedil;lyk sa&ccedil; d&uuml;z&uuml;mine
&yacute;a&yacute;randa,&nbsp;<b>seboreiki t&auml;&ccedil;&nbsp;</b>di&yacute;il&yacute;&auml;r&nbsp;.&nbsp;Seborriki
tegmiller simmetrik &yacute;agda&yacute;da &yacute;erle&#351;ip biler.&nbsp;</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:14.0pt;margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:
-.25in;line-height:normal'><span style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;
color:black'>·<span style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><b><span style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>Ka&#351;&#305;nt&#305;&nbsp;</span></b><span style='font-size:
13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>&yacute;erlerinde
seboreik t&auml;sir.&nbsp;</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><span style='font-size:13.5pt;
font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>Leiner keseli - Mousse bilen
&ccedil;aga gyzzyrma d&ouml;redip, limfa d&uuml;w&uuml;nlerini ulaldyp,
bedeni&#328; agramyny peseldip biler.</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><span style='font-size:13.5pt;
font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>Seborriki dermatit
&yacute;oka&#351;ma&yacute;ar we hatda &ccedil;agalarda-da &ouml;l&uuml;me
seb&auml;p bolma&yacute;ar.&nbsp;N&auml;saglarda i&#328; uly
o&#328;a&yacute;syzlyk, gyjyndyrma we derini&#328; da&#351;ky
g&ouml;rn&uuml;&#351;ini&#328; &yacute;aramazla&#351;magy bilen
&yacute;&uuml;ze &ccedil;yk&yacute;ar.</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><b><span style='font-size:18.0pt;
font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>Keseli&#328; diagnozy</span></b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><b><span style='font-size:13.5pt;
font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>Sorag we g&ouml;zleg</span></b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><span style='font-size:13.5pt;
font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>Seboreiki dermatiti&#328;
diagnozyna dermatolog jogapk&auml;rdir.&nbsp;Adat&ccedil;a diagnoz
go&yacute;mak kyn d&auml;l, munu&#328; &uuml;&ccedil;in lukman
d&ouml;k&uuml;nm&auml;ni &uuml;ns bilen g&ouml;zden
ge&ccedil;irmeli.&nbsp;D&uuml;w&uuml;rtikleri&#328;
&yacute;erle&#351;&yacute;&auml;n &yacute;erine we olary&#328;
h&auml;si&yacute;etine g&ouml;r&auml; lukman dogry diagnoz go&yacute;ar.</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><b><span style='font-size:13.5pt;
font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>Laboratori&yacute;a barlagy</span></b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><span style='font-size:13.5pt;
font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>Laboratori&yacute;a
g&ouml;zlegleri seboreiki dermatiti&#328; diagnozynda a&yacute;gytly rol
o&yacute;nama&yacute;ar we tebigatda k&ouml;mek&ccedil;i bolup
dur&yacute;ar.&nbsp;Leiner-Mousse keseli bolan &ccedil;agalary&#328;
&yacute;agda&yacute;yna baha bermek &uuml;&ccedil;in kliniki gan synagyndan
ge&ccedil;&yacute;&auml;rler (ganazlygy kesgitl&auml;p bol&yacute;ar), umumy pe&#351;ew
synagy we gandaky belok we demir derejelerini &ouml;wrenmek.</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><b><span style='font-size:13.5pt;
font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>Funksi&yacute;a,
radiasi&yacute;a we instrumental diagnostika</span></b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><span style='font-size:13.5pt;
font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>Seboreiki dermatit bilen saz
gurallary, h&ouml;kmany suratda h&ouml;kmany d&auml;l.&nbsp;K&auml;wagt
diagnozy tassyklamak&nbsp;&uuml;&ccedil;in mikroskop astynda derini&#328;&nbsp;<b>bir&nbsp;</b>b&ouml;legini&nbsp;<b>gistologiki
g&ouml;zden ge&ccedil;irmek&nbsp;</b>ge&ccedil;iril&yacute;&auml;r&nbsp;,
onu&#328; &uuml;st&uuml;nde sebaceous bezlerine wilkalary,
le&yacute;kositleri&#328; &yacute;ygnanmagyny, epidermisi&#328; birneme
&ccedil;i&#351;megini we k&ouml;melek &ouml;&yacute;j&uuml;klerini tapyp
bilersi&#328;iz.&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><b><span style='font-size:18.0pt;
font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>Bejergi</span></b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><b><span style='font-size:13.5pt;
font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>Bejergi maksatlary</span></b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><span style='font-size:13.5pt;
font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>Seboreiki dermatiti bejermekde
esasy wezipe derini&#328; da&#351;ky g&ouml;rn&uuml;&#351;ini
gowula&#351;dyrmak, tereziden we kepekden dynmak we &ccedil;i&#351;megi
duruzmakdyr.&nbsp;&#350;e&yacute;le hem gijilew&uuml;k &yacute;aly alamatlardan
dynmak we k&ouml;melek &yacute;okan&ccedil;lyklaryny &yacute;ok etmek
m&ouml;h&uuml;mdir.</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><b><span style='font-size:13.5pt;
font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>Durmu&#351; &yacute;oly we
gurallar</span></b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><span style='font-size:13.5pt;
font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>Bejergide arassa&ccedil;ylyk
m&ouml;h&uuml;m rol o&yacute;na&yacute;ar.&nbsp;Ilyagly deri &uuml;&ccedil;in
&yacute;&ouml;rite &ouml;n&uuml;mleri&#328; k&ouml;megi bilen amala
a&#351;yrylsa has gowudyr.&nbsp;Kepek we kell&auml;ni&#328; sebore&yacute;asyny
bejermekde &yacute;&ouml;rite arassa&ccedil;ylyk &#351;ampunlary we
los&yacute;onlar ulanyl&yacute;ar.</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><b><span style='font-size:13.5pt;
font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>Dermanlar</span></b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><span style='font-size:13.5pt;
font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>Seboreiki dermatit
&uuml;&ccedil;in dermanlar i&ccedil;erde we i&ccedil;erde
ulanyl&yacute;ar.&nbsp;Dermanlar &ccedil;i&#351;m&auml;, gyjyndyrmalara,
antifungal seri&#351;delere gar&#351;y ulanyl&yacute;ar.</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:
-.25in;line-height:normal'><span style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;
color:black'>·<span style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><b><span style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>Gl&yacute;ukokortikosteroidler&nbsp;</span></b><span
style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>esasan
melhem, krem &#8203;&#8203;we los&yacute;on g&ouml;rn&uuml;&#351;inde
k&ouml;plen&ccedil; deride gaty terezini ered&yacute;&auml;n salisil
tur&#351;usy bilen bilelikde ulanyl&yacute;an &ccedil;i&#351;m&auml; gar&#351;y
t&auml;sirli dermanlardyr.&nbsp;Belli bir dermany sa&yacute;lamagy lukmana
tab&#351;yrmak has gowudyr, seb&auml;bi bu esasan
&ccedil;i&#351;m&auml;ni&#328; agyrlygyna baglydyr.&nbsp;</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:-.25in;line-height:
normal'><span style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;color:black'>·<span
style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><b><span style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>Antifungal dermanlar&nbsp;</span></b><span style='font-size:13.5pt;
font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>- kesel kell&auml; t&auml;sir
etse, esasan krem, jel, melhem &yacute;a-da &#351;ampun
g&ouml;rn&uuml;&#351;inde ulanyl&yacute;ar.&nbsp;Gaty dermatitde lukman
tabletkalarda &yacute;a-da sanjymlarda antifungal dermanlary bell&auml;p
biler.&nbsp;</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:-.25in;line-height:
normal'><span style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;color:black'>·<span
style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><b><span style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>Sink pirition&nbsp;</span></b><span style='font-size:13.5pt;
font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>antifungal we&nbsp;<b>sebore&yacute;a&nbsp;</b>gar&#351;y
seri&#351;dedir.&nbsp;Deride &ccedil;u&#328;&#328;ur arala&#351;yp,
&yacute;olda patogen bakteri&yacute;alary we k&ouml;melekleri &yacute;ok
ed&yacute;&auml;r.&nbsp;&#350;ampunlar, kremler, aerozollar
g&ouml;rn&uuml;&#351;inde ulanyl&yacute;ar.&nbsp;</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:-.25in;line-height:
normal'><span style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;color:black'>·<span
style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><b><span style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>Emol&yacute;entler&nbsp;</span></b><span style='font-size:13.5pt;
font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>- &ouml;s&uuml;mlik
&yacute;agy, nebit jeli we &#351;.m. &ccedil;agalarda sebore&yacute;any
a&yacute;yrmak, terezini &yacute;um&#351;atmak &uuml;&ccedil;in
ulanyl&yacute;ar.&nbsp;</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:14.0pt;margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:
-.25in;line-height:normal'><span style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;
color:black'>·<span style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><b><span style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>Antihistaminikler&nbsp;</span></b><span style='font-size:13.5pt;
font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>- Dilden kabul edilende,&nbsp;<b>gijilew&uuml;kden&nbsp;</b>dynmaga
k&ouml;mek ed&yacute;&auml;r.&nbsp;</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><b><span style='font-size:13.5pt;
font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>Amallar</span></b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><span style='font-size:13.5pt;
font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>Sebore&yacute;any
bejermegi&#328; bejeri&#351; usullaryndan fototerapi&yacute;a k&ouml;mek
ed&yacute;&auml;r - t&auml;sir edilen deri &yacute;erlerini &yacute;&ouml;rite
sa&yacute;lanan spektri&#328; &yacute;agtylygy bilen
&#351;&ouml;hlelendir&yacute;&auml;r.&nbsp;Amallar hepdede 3 gezek 8
hepd&auml;ni&#328; dowamynda &yacute;a-da keseli&#328; da&#351;ky
g&ouml;rn&uuml;&#351;leri &yacute;ok edil&yacute;&auml;n&ccedil;&auml; amala
a&#351;yryl&yacute;ar.</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><b><span style='font-size:13.5pt;
font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>Hirurgiki amallar</span></b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><span style='font-size:13.5pt;
font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>Seboreiki dermatit
&uuml;&ccedil;in hirurgiki bejergisi ulanylma&yacute;ar.</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><b><span style='font-size:13.5pt;
font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>Durmu&#351;y&#328; hilini
dikeltmek we gowula&#351;dyrmak</span></b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><span style='font-size:13.5pt;
font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>Seboreiki dermatit bilen
&yacute;a&#351;a&yacute;&#351;y&#328; hiline, derini&#328;, kepeki&#328; we
gyjyndyrmadan ba&#351;ga-da t&auml;sir edilme&yacute;&auml;r.&nbsp;1-2
bejeri&#351; kursy o&#328;at kosmetiki t&auml;sir ed&yacute;&auml;r,
&#351;ondan so&#328; derini&#328; &yacute;agda&yacute;yny gowy saklamak
&uuml;&ccedil;in g&uuml;ndelik arassa&ccedil;ylyk &yacute;eterlikdir.&nbsp;&#350;ampunlar
&uuml;&ccedil;in selen sulfidi, sink piritiony, &ccedil;a&yacute; agajyny&#328;
&yacute;agy &yacute;a-da k&ouml;m&uuml;r &ccedil;orbasy bolan &#351;ampunlar
ulanyl&yacute;ar.</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><b><span style='font-size:18.0pt;
font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>M&uuml;mkin kyn&ccedil;ylyklar</span></b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><span style='font-size:13.5pt;
font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>D&uuml;zg&uuml;n bol&#351;y
&yacute;aly, seboreiki dermatiti&#328; kyn&ccedil;ylyklary
&yacute;ok.&nbsp;Se&yacute;rek &yacute;agda&yacute;larda
g&uuml;&yacute;&ccedil;li dyrna&ccedil;ak bilen ikinji derejeli
infeksi&yacute;a go&#351;ulyp biler we supurasi&yacute;a ba&#351;lap
biler.&nbsp;Kell&auml;ni&#328; sebore&yacute;asy bolan k&auml;bir adamlarda,
bejerilmese, kesel &#351;e&yacute;le bir g&uuml;&yacute;&ccedil;lenip biler
welin, seboreiki alopezi&yacute;a (alopeki&yacute;a) seb&auml;p bol&yacute;ar.</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><b><span style='font-size:18.0pt;
font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>&Ouml;&#328;&uuml;ni aly&#351;
&ccedil;&auml;releri</span></b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><span style='font-size:13.5pt;
font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>Seboreiki dermatiti&#328;
&ouml;&#328;&uuml;ni almak &uuml;&ccedil;in &yacute;&ouml;rite
&ccedil;&auml;reler &yacute;ok, adaty arassa&ccedil;ylyk amallary
&yacute;eterlikdir.</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><b><span style='font-size:18.0pt;
font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>&Ccedil;aklama</span></b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><span style='font-size:13.5pt;
font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>Seboreiki dermatiti&#328;
&ccedil;aklamasy amatly, kesel k&ouml;plen&ccedil; &ouml;z-&ouml;z&uuml;nden
a&yacute;ryl&yacute;ar.&nbsp;&Ccedil;agalarda dikeldi&#351; birn&auml;&ccedil;e
hepde &yacute;a-da birn&auml;&ccedil;e a&yacute;y&#328; i&ccedil;inde
&yacute;&uuml;ze &ccedil;yk&yacute;ar.&nbsp;Uly adamlarda bu kesel
&ouml;m&uuml;rbo&yacute;y dowam edip biler, wagtal-wagtal
erbetle&#351;&yacute;&auml;r, &yacute;&ouml;ne adat&ccedil;a bejerg&auml; jogap
gowy bol&yacute;ar.</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><b><span style='font-size:18.0pt;
font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>Lukmandan ha&yacute;sy
soraglary bermeli?</span></b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-left:71.9pt;text-indent:
-.25in;line-height:normal'><span style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>1.<span style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>Gyjyndyrmany we keseli&#328; be&yacute;leki
g&ouml;rn&uuml;&#351;lerini n&auml;dip azaltmaly?</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-left:71.9pt;text-indent:-.25in;line-height:
normal'><span style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>2.<span style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>Special&ouml;rite di&yacute;eta e&yacute;ermelimi?</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-left:71.9pt;text-indent:-.25in;line-height:
normal'><span style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>3.<span style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>Derini bejermek &ouml;n&uuml;mlerini n&auml;dip sa&yacute;lamaly?</span></p>

